com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance

Class PercentageFromAuctionPriceFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance.ComplianceFilter
      • com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance.PercentageFromAuctionPriceFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IComplianceFilter, IConfigurableContainer

    public class PercentageFromAuctionPriceFilter
extends ComplianceFilter
implements IConfigurableContainer
    PercentageFromAuctionPriceFilter is a compliance filter that checks for the order is no more than an specified percentage away (measured as an absolute value) from the indicative auction price. It is designed to capture orders entered in error or those with no likelihood of execution.
    Author:
    Tom Vasak
